#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: eventadmin-volunteer-management.php
msgid "EventAdmin – Volunteer Management"
msgstr "EventAdmin – Volunteer Management"

#. Description of the plugin
#: eventadmin-volunteer-management.php
msgid ""
"Manage volunteers for events directly in WordPress. Create and schedule "
"shifts, allow volunteers to sign up and cancel independently, and configure "
"individual rules – e.g., maximum shifts per person per year."
msgstr ""
"Beheer Volunteers voor evenementen rechtstreeks in WordPress. Maak diensten "
"aan en plan ze in, laat Volunteers zich zelfstandig aanmelden en afmelden, "
"en configureer individuele regels – bijv. maximale diensten per persoon per "
"jaar."

