"automated spam registrations."
msgstr ""
"Voegt een CAPTCHA-uitdaging toe aan het registratieformulier om "
"geautomatiseerde spamregistraties te blokkeren."

#: includes/admin/settings.php:367
msgid "CAPTCHA site key"
msgstr "CAPTCHA-sitesleutel"

#: includes/admin/settings.php:370
msgid "Get your keys from the provider's admin console."
msgstr "Haal uw sleutels op uit de beheerconsole van de aanbieder."

#: includes/admin/settings.php:378
msgid "CAPTCHA secret key"
msgstr "CAPTCHA-geheime sleutel"

#: includes/admin/settings.php:388
msgid "reCAPTCHA v3 score threshold"
msgstr "reCAPTCHA v3 scoredrempel"

#: includes/admin/settings.php:392
msgid ""
"Scores below this value are treated as bots (0.0 = all pass, 1.0 = all "
"blocked). Default: 0.5. Only applies to reCAPTCHA v3."
msgstr ""
"Scores onder deze waarde worden als bots beschouwd (0.0 = alles door, 1.0 = "
"alles geblokkeerd). Standaard: 0.5. Geldt alleen voor reCAPTCHA v3."

#: includes/admin/settings.php:400
msgid "Volunteer Shift Selector"
msgstr "Dienstkiezer voor vrijwilligers"

#: includes/admin/settings.php:407
msgid "Show full shifts to volunteers"
msgstr "Volle diensten tonen aan Volunteers"

#: includes/admin/settings.php:411
msgid ""
"If enabled, a \"Full shifts\" section is shown on the volunteer shift "
"selector page."
